      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_d2d94059bd4479f52a54df99a29f93bd">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Collection of Oxford and Cambridge Bookplates, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <processinfo id="aspace_15938e85a5d4de421816598a1fccd8ea">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Some materials included in this collection indicate the provenance of the following collections: Irene D. Andrews Pace, Dr. J. S. Pearson, and A. Bernard C. K. Keeves.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_73a241c3fd77c89224b97d26f203a734">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection includes bookplates for the various residential colleges affiliated with the University of Oxford or the University of Cambridge, both of which are located in England.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_d4f6d982e4d84b5b00041744e0e674db">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Bookplates – Oxford. II. Bookplates – Cambridge.</p>  
      </arrangement>
