               <scopecontent id="aspace_b9a6c1a64d1d7d2cde2975eaa52eafc1">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>This folder contains 45 bookplates which were all housed in a portfolio labeled "Bookplates of Colleges of Oxford." The portfolio, individual mounts, and bookplates often bear the collector's stamp of A. Bernard C. K. Keeves as well as annotations in his hand. The portfolio also contains a couple of examples of supralibros, which are ex-libris designs stamped on the exterior of a book cover.</p>
               </scopecontent>
